@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_cweofc(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = 0.93
    tmp = ((v1 * 0.76) * wp.abs(wp.exp(v0 + 0.74)))
    v1 = ((wp.sin(v1 + 0.93) + (v0 + 0.79 + v2 + 0.47)) - ((v0 + 0.09 * tmp + 0.01) * (tmp + 0.48 + v0 + 0.68)))
    data[tid] = v0
